column5: So I was up in Phelpston for my bro-in-laws b-day and we went over to his buddy's for a beer and ended up meeting another OFC'er named Jeff, but I can't remember his OFC name.  Either way, nice to meet you and I hope we can get out fishing some time.
Is it the palace in phelpston or is it the tavern?  I can't remember.  I drive past Phelpston everyday. I carpool with a friend from Elmvale.
we weren't at the bar, I think it's long gone? we were at a home in the older homes on the South side of town.

The Palace is in Elmvale and is still going strong.  The Phelpston reopened just before Christmas and is called Kelly's New Phelpston.  It went through a makeover just before Christmas and the Kellys are doing a great job running the place.
